	(1, 'TechSync ChronoPro X: Precision Digital Watch', 'techsync-chronopro-x-precision-digital-watch', 'DW2023M', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2, 'TechSync ChronoPro X, a cutting-edge digital watch designed for the contemporary adventurer. This high-performance timepiece seamlessly combines.', '<p>Key Features:</p><p><span style="font-size: 1rem;"><b>Precision Timekeeping:</b> The ChronoPro X is equipped with state-of-the-art quartz movement, ensuring unparalleled accuracy in timekeeping. Whether youre navigating the urban jungle or embarking on a wilderness expedition, trust the precision of TechSync.</span><br></p><p><span style="font-size: 1rem;"><b>Digital Display Excellence:</b> The vibrant LCD display offers crystal-clear visibility, presenting time, date, and additional features with sharp clarity. Effortlessly toggle between various functions using the intuitive interface.</span><br></p><p><span style="font-size: 1rem;"><b>Rugged Durability:</b> Engineered for durability, the ChronoPro X boasts a robust yet lightweight construction. The scratch-resistant mineral crystal and water-resistant design make it a reliable companion for any environment.</span><br></p><p><span style="font-size: 1rem;"><b>Smart Functionality:</b> Stay connected and organized with smart features such as alarms, stopwatch, and a backlight for low-light conditions. The watch also includes a calendar function, ensuring youre well-prepared for every occasion.</span><br></p><p><span style="font-size: 1rem;"><b>Sleek Design:</b> The modern design of the ChronoPro X combines form and function seamlessly. The sleek profile, complemented by a stainless steel case and comfortable silicone strap, makes it suitable for both formal and casual settings.</span><br></p><p><span style="font-size: 1rem;"><b>Long-lasting Battery Life:</b> Say goodbye to frequent charging. The ChronoPro X is engineered for efficiency, providing extended battery life to keep up with your dynamic lifestyle.</span><br></p>', 2, '1-1702299064.jpg', 2, 2, '50', 1, 40, 750.00, 450.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '2024-01-22 01:05:00', '2024-01-22 01:05:00'),
	(2, 'HyperGrip Pro Gaming Pad', 'hypergrip-pro-gaming-pad', 'GP2026A', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2, 'HyperGrip Pro, the ultimate game pad designed to elevate your gaming experience to new heights. Engineered for precision, comfort, and versatility.', '<p><b>Key Features:</b></p><p><span style="font-size: 1rem;"><b>Responsive Precision:</b></span><br></p><p><span style="font-size: 1rem;">The HyperGrip Pro boasts ultra-responsive buttons and analog sticks, providing gamers with unparalleled control and accuracy. Every press and movement translates seamlessly into the virtual world, giving you the edge in fast-paced action.</span><br></p><p><b>Ergonomic Design:</b></p><p><span style="font-size: 1rem;">Say goodbye to hand fatigue with the ergonomic design of the HyperGrip Pro. Comfort is king, and this game pad is sculpted to fit naturally in your hands, ensuring extended gaming sessions without discomfort.</span><br></p><p><b>Customizable Controls:</b></p><p><span style="font-size: 1rem;">Tailor the game pad to your playstyle with customizable controls. Easily remap buttons and adjust sensitivity to match the demands of different games, putting the power of customization at your fingertips.</span><br></p><p><b>Versatile Compatibility:</b></p><p><span style="font-size: 1rem;">The HyperGrip Pro is designed for universal compatibility, seamlessly connecting to a variety of gaming platforms, including PC, consoles, and mobile devices. Enjoy the same exceptional performance across all your gaming devices.</span><br></p><p><b>Wireless Freedom:</b></p><p><span style="font-size: 1rem;">Cut the cords and enjoy wireless freedom with the HyperGrip Pro. Whether youre lounging on the couch or engaging in an intense gaming session at your desk, the wireless connectivity ensures a hassle-free and immersive experience.</span><br></p><p><b>Immersive Feedback:</b></p><p><span style="font-size: 1rem;">Feel the action with immersive haptic feedback. The HyperGrip Pro provides tactile sensations that enhance your gaming experience, allowing you to feel every explosion, hit, or subtle nuance within the game.</span><br></p><p><b>Stylish Aesthetics:</b></p><p><span style="font-size: 1rem;">Elevate your gaming setup with the sleek and stylish design of the HyperGrip Pro. Backlit buttons add a futuristic touch, while the overall aesthetic reflects the cutting-edge technology packed into this high-performance game pad.</span><br></p>', 7, '7-1702302730.jpg', 2, 2, '0', 1, 40, 500.00, 600.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '2024-01-22 01:05:00', '2024-01-22 01:05:00'),
	(3, 'Essentials Harmony Elevate Your Home', 'essentials-harmony-elevate-your-home', 'HS2234G', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2, 'A suite of meticulously crafted household products designed to seamlessly integrate into your daily routine, bringing efficiency.', '<p><b>Effortless Cleaning with Radiance Broom:</b></p><p><span style="font-size: 1rem;">The Radiance Broom isnt just a cleaning tool; its a household hero. Crafted with precision bristles and an ergonomic handle, it effortlessly sweeps away dirt, leaving your floors gleaming. Embrace the joy of efficient cleaning with this essential household companion.</span><br></p><p><b>Culinary Mastery with CulinaChef Knife Set:</b></p><p><span style="font-size: 1rem;">Unleash your inner chef with the CulinaChef Knife Set. Precision-engineered blades meet ergonomic handles for a perfect balance of form and function. Elevate your culinary creations and make every meal preparation a work of art.</span><br></p><p><b>Laundry Bliss with FreshGlow Fabric Softener:</b></p><p><span style="font-size: 1rem;">Transform your laundry routine with FreshGlow Fabric Softener. Indulge in the luxurious softness it brings to your clothes while enjoying the invigorating fragrance that lingers. Rediscover the joy of wearing garments that feel as good as they look.</span><br></p><p><b>Smart Storage with SpaceSaver Organizers:</b></p><p><span style="font-size: 1rem;">Tame the clutter and reclaim your space with SpaceSaver Organizers. These sleek, stackable wonders maximize storage efficiency, turning chaotic spaces into organized sanctuaries. Experience the liberation of a tidy home without compromising on style.</span><br></p><p><b>Revolutionize Cleaning with PureMist Cleaning Spray:</b></p><p><span style="font-size: 1rem;">Introducing PureMist Cleaning Spray, a game-changer in household cleaning. This eco-friendly powerhouse effortlessly tackles grime and germs, leaving surfaces sparkling clean and your home smelling fresh. Embrace the future of clean with this essential addition to your cleaning arsenal.</span><br></p><p><b>Tranquil Ambiance with ZenAura Oil Diffuser:</b></p><p><span style="font-size: 1rem;">Transform your living space into a haven of tranquility with the ZenAura Oil Diffuser. Elegant design meets therapeutic functionality, providing a soothing ambiance with your favorite essential oils. Elevate your home environment with this serene addition.</span><br></p>', 4, '3-1702311850.jpg', 2, 2, '0', 1, 100, 750.00, 550.00, 0.00, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '2024-01-22 01:05:00', '2024-01-22 01:05:00'),
