	(6, 'Antique Products To Explore History.', 'antique-products-to-explore-history', 'BP2023HK', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2, 'Indulge in the luxury of our Radiant Glow Skincare Set, a meticulously curated collection of beauty products designed to nourish, rejuvenate, and enhance your natural beauty. Crafted with precision and infused with the finest ingredients, this set is your ultimate companion for a radiant and flawless complexion.', '<p>Key Features:</p><p><br></p><p>Revitalizing Cleanser:</p><p>Begin your skincare ritual with our gentle yet effective revitalizing cleanser. Enriched with botanical extracts and antioxidants, it effortlessly removes impurities, leaving your skin refreshed and ready for the next steps.</p><p><br></p><p>Hydrating Facial Toner:</p><p>Our hydrating facial toner is a burst of hydration for your skin. Formulated with floral waters and essential nutrients, it restores the skinspH balance, prepping it for optimal absorption of subsequent skincare products.</p><p><br></p><p>Nourishing Day Cream:</p><p>Experience the embrace of our nourishing day cream, a lightweight and hydrating formula that provides all-day moisture. Packed with vitamins and SPF protection, it defends your skin against environmental stressors while leaving it silky smooth.</p><p><br></p><p>Rejuvenating Night Serum:</p><p>Unwind with our rejuvenating night serum, a potent elixir that works while you sleep. Infused with anti-aging ingredients, it helps reduce fine lines and promotes cell renewal, revealing a more youthful and radiant complexion by morning.</p><p><br></p><p>Eye Brightening Treatment:</p><p>Banish signs of fatigue with our eye brightening treatment. Specially formulated for the delicate eye area, it reduces puffiness, minimizes dark circles, and revitalizes tired eyes for a refreshed and awakened look.</p><p><br></p><p>Pampering Face Mask:</p><p>Treat yourself to a spa-like experience with our pampering face mask. Formulated with natural clays and botanical extracts, it detoxifies, hydrates, and leaves your skin feeling luxuriously soft and revitalized.</p>', 3, '6-1702365568.jpg', 1, 1, '50', 1, 100, NULL, NULL, 500.00, '2023-11-28 15:24:00', '2030-12-31 17:59:00', 1, NULL, '2024-01-22 01:05:00', '2024-01-22 01:05:00'),
