	(17, 6, 'code-editor', 'a9c63c9', '{"content":"<p><b><span style=\\"font-size: 24px;\\">Welcome to <u>BidOut<\\/u> Help Center<\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p><span style=\\"font-size: 1rem;\\">Welcome to the BidOut Help Center! Whether youre a seasoned bidder or a first-time user, this page is designed to provide you with the information you need to navigate our platform effectively. If you have any questions or concerns that are not addressed here.<\\/span><br><\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><b><span style=\\"font-size: 18px;\\"><u>Getting Started<\\/u><\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p><b>1. Creating an Account:<\\/b><\\/p><p>To start bidding on exciting items, you need to create an account. Check our guide on how to set up your account securely and efficiently.<\\/p><p><b style=\\"font-size: 1rem;\\">2. Navigating the Dashboard:<\\/b><br><\\/p><p>Learn how to explore auctions, view item details, and manage your bids through our intuitive user dashboard.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><b><span style=\\"font-size: 18px;\\"><u>Placing Bids<\\/u><\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p><b>1. How to Place a Bid:<\\/b><\\/p><p>Step-by-step instructions on placing bids to ensure youre in the running for your desired items.<\\/p><p><b style=\\"font-size: 1rem;\\">2. Automatic Bidding (Proxy Bidding):<\\/b><br><\\/p><p>Understand how our automatic bidding system works to help you stay ahead in auctions.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><b><span style=\\"font-size: 18px;\\"><u>Managing Your Account<\\/u><\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p><b>1. Updating Account Information:<\\/b><\\/p><p>Learn how to keep your account details up-to-date, including changing your password and updating payment information.<\\/p><p><b style=\\"font-size: 1rem;\\">2. Notifications and Alerts:<\\/b><br><\\/p><p>Customize your notification preferences to stay informed about auction updates, bid status, and more.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><b><span style=\\"font-size: 18px;\\"><u>Selling Items<\\/u><\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p><b>1. Listing Items for Auction:<\\/b><\\/p><p>If youre looking to sell, check our guide on creating compelling listings and attracting potential buyers.<\\/p><p><b style=\\"font-size: 1rem;\\">2. Managing Your Listings:<\\/b><br><\\/p><p>Learn how to edit, renew, or end your auctions, and track the performance of your listed items.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><b><span style=\\"font-size: 18px;\\"><u>Payments and Fees<\\/u><\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p><b>1. Understanding Fees:<\\/b><\\/p><p>Get an overview of our fee structure, including listing fees, final value fees, and other applicable charges.<\\/p><p><span style=\\"font-size: 1rem;\\"><b>2. Making Payments:<\\/b><\\/span><br><\\/p><p>Guidance on making secure and seamless payments for your won items.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><b><span style=\\"font-size: 18px;\\"><u>Troubleshooting and FAQs<\\/u><\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p><b>1. Common Issues:<\\/b><\\/p><p>Find solutions to common problems users encounter during auctions and bidding.<\\/p><p><b style=\\"font-size: 1rem;\\">2. Frequently Asked Questions:<\\/b><br><\\/p><p>Explore our comprehensive FAQs for quick answers to the most commonly asked questions.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><b><u><span style=\\"font-size: 18px;\\">Policies and Guidelines<\\/span><\\/u><\\/b><\\/p><p><b>1. Terms and Conditions:<\\/b><\\/p><p>Review our terms and conditions to understand the rules governing the use of our platform.<\\/p><p><span style=\\"font-size: 1rem;\\"><b>2. Privacy Policy:<\\/b><\\/span><br><\\/p><p>Learn about how we handle your personal information and ensure your privacy.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><b><span style=\\"font-size: 18px;\\">Contact Us<\\/span><\\/b><\\/p><p>Still Need Help?<\\/p><p>If you cant find the information youre looking for, or if you have specific concerns, feel free to reach out to our support team at <b>info@bidout.com .<\\/b><\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>Thank you for choosing <b>BidOut<\\/b>! Happy bidding!<\\/p>"}', 2, 1, '2024-01-22 01:05:00', '2024-01-22 01:05:00'),
	(18, 7, 'faq', 'b36430a', '{"main_title":"Frequently Asked Questions","faqs":{"1":{"title":"How can I place a bid on an item?","description":"Bidding is easy! Simply navigate to the item youreinterested in, enter your bid amount, and click the \\"Place Bid\\" button. Make sure to review your bid before confirming. Youll receive real-time updates on the bidding status of the item."},"2":{"title":"What payment methods are accepted?","description":"We accept various secure payment methods, including major credit cards and digital payment options. Payment details will be provided at the end of a successful auction. Rest assured, all transactions are encrypted for your security."},"3":{"title":"Can I track the status of my bids?","description":"Yes, you can track your bids in real-time. Visit the \\"My Bids\\" section in your account to view the items youve bid on, their current status, and whether you are the highest bidder."},"4":{"title":"How can I ensure the authenticity of items?","description":"We prioritize transparency and authenticity. Each item is accompanied by detailed descriptions and, when available, provenance information. Our team thoroughly vets items to ensure their legitimacy and quality."},"5":{"title":"Is my personal information secure?","description":"Yes, we take the security of your information seriously. Our website employs encryption protocols to safeguard your personal and payment details. Refer to our Privacy Policy for more details on data protection measures."}}}', 1, 1, '2024-01-22 01:05:00', '2024-01-22 01:05:00'),
